desc: 약화 부상 마비에 대한 저항력 증가

dictionary.lore: An amulet called the "Royal Light," named after one of the two lights said to be given off by kings. It is said that this light protects the one who governs the world from weakness, injury, and paralysis. Remnants of what was engraved on the back by the amulet's creator, Median, read, "I... chase... ideals. In... ...I believe."

name: 왕광 메디안
